\id 1KI Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h 1 MANGHAI
\toc1 1 MANGHAI
\toc2 1Manghai
\toc3 1Mg
\mt1 MANGHAI CABU
\mt3 A Pacuek Nah
\mt4 (The First Book of the Kings)
\is2 Manghai Cabu A Pacuek Kawng
\im Manghai Cabu (I neh II) he a cuek vaengah pakhat lamni rhen a om. Israel kah khokhuen kawng te David tue lamloh Jerusalem poci tih Babylon la pilnam a poeng hil kah a kawng te a tael. Samuel cabu dongah tah Pathen olngai neh altha rhoek kawng te a tueng sak. Manghai cabu a pacuek dongah David kah a hnuktloih, Solomon manghai la om tih Jerusalem bawkim a saknah, a nawnnah kawng om. Cabu a rhakthuem vaengah tah Israel ram panit la a rheknah khawng, Tlangpuei te Israel ram, Tuithim te Judah ram la a om kawng a tael. Tonghma Elijah kah pongthohnah kawng a tael. 586-561\sc b.c\sc* tluk vaengkah Judah neh Israel manghai rhoek kawng te hmaih a tueng sak. He cabu he 531\sc b.c\sc* tluk vaengah hekah cabu he a daek.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 Solomon manghai \ior 1. 1—2. 46\ior*
\io1 Solomon kut hmuikah Israel\ior 3. 1—11. 43\ior*
\io1 Ram Paekboenah \ior 12. 1—22. 53\ior*
\c 1
\s1 David kah Hnukkhueng
\p 
